ActNational Capital Act
SubjectLease with Momentous Corporation ** NCC **
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant one option of five years, commencing on September 1, 2018, to renew an existing five-year lease with MOMENTOUS CORPORATION to occupy third floor office space and lower level storage space in the building located at 12-18 York Street, in Ottawa.
